00:57.933 --> 01:02.933 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: We are now
on the eve of seeing a Senate
proposal for health care,

01:12.100 --> 01:14.600 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
including replacing the
Affordable Care Act.

01:14.600 --> 01:18.300 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
Republican leaders plan
to release their bill
tomorrow, after working
on it behind closed

01:18.300 --> 01:20.333 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
doors for weeks.

01:20.333 --> 01:24.933 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Late today, The Washington Post
reported a draft bill largely
mirrors the House's version,

01:27.000 --> 01:28.966 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
but with some notable changes.

01:28.966 --> 01:32.766 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
