that restricts federally
subsidized health plans
from covering abortions.

01:38.633 --> 01:40.700 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
Lisa Desjardins joins me now.

01:40.700 --> 01:44.900 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
