senators will gather
for this exact reason.

01:57.866 --> 01:59.100 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
When will we see it?

01:59.100 --> 02:00.733 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
When will the public see it?

02:00.733 --> 02:04.500 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Republicans tell me that is
at the same time, 9:30 a.m.

02:04.500 --> 02:05.700 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
