told me he sees what he
hears as Obamacare-lite.

02:26.033 --> 02:28.333 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
And another senator, Ron
Johnson of Wisconsin,
told me he's concerned.

02:28.333 --> 02:30.433 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
He asked for more time
to review this bill.

02:30.433 --> 02:33.966 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
He said a vote next week,
as is planned, is too soon.

02:33.966 --> 02:37.966 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
