two holy mosques, King
Salman bin Abdulaziz

06:05.333 --> 06:07.366 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
Al Saud, has issued
royal decrees.

06:07.366 --> 06:10.700 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
HARI SREENIVASAN: The
announcement was read
on state television.

06:10.700 --> 06:15.700 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
