with the Iranians.

07:25.100 --> 07:30.000 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
PETER WALDMAN: His confrontation
with Iran across the Persian
Gulf is a bit dangerous.

07:31.966 --> 07:35.866 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
