11:47.466 --> 11:51.200 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEANETTE MANFRA, Department
of Homeland Security:
As of right now we have
evidence of 21 states

11:51.200 --> 11:55.266 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
