12:01.600 --> 12:03.633 align:left position:25%,start line:86.67% size:75%
JEANETTE MANFRA:
That is correct.

12:03.633 --> 12:07.066 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: In a separate
