12:49.833 --> 12:54.400 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
This afternoon, we heard
multiple DHS officials
say that they have
more and more evidence

12:56.500 --> 12:59.200 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
that Russia tried to interfere
in the campaigns or interfere
in the election systems in 21

12:59.200 --> 13:01.300 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
different states.

13:01.300 --> 13:03.300 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And while they stress that
none of the votes were flipped
in any of these states, they

13:03.300 --> 13:07.600 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
did say that some of these
intrusions kind of made it
past of the security systems.

13:07.600 --> 13:12.600 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So, my question is, why
not release the information
on which states or which
localities were compromised?

13:13.066 --> 13:14.600 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
SEN.

13:14.600 --> 13:15.533 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JAMES LANKFORD (R), Oklahoma: So
the FBI has a very clear policy.

13:15.533 --> 13:17.633 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
They don't expose victims.

13:17.633 --> 13:20.100 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And they consider these
states to be victims of an
intrusion on the outside.

13:20.100 --> 13:23.800 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
If the states want to be able
to say that or if they want
to be able to release that,

13:23.800 --> 13:25.933 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
obviously, they're
welcome to do.

13:25.933 --> 13:30.666 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
But for a location that
was actually attacked by
an outside force they're
not going to release

13:31.133 --> 13:32.333 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
it.

13:32.333 --> 13:34.433 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
Some of those will
continue to come out.

13:34.433 --> 13:36.233 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Some of those states will say,
yes, we're one of the states,
and the list will eventually

13:36.233 --> 13:38.333 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
come out.

13:38.333 --> 13:40.300 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: You agree it's
