13:42.633 --> 13:43.866 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
SEN.

13:43.866 --> 13:45.866 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
JAMES LANKFORD:
Absolutely, it is.

13:45.866 --> 13:48.566 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
There were really three
