Committee and I have
been very aware of it.

14:09.066 --> 14:11.600 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
I think more Americans are
aware of what is going on, as
we try to engage our federal

14:11.600 --> 14:15.900 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
government to be able to
step up to the level of
risk that we really face.

14:15.900 --> 14:20.066 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
A lot of states have become
more aware of it, and their
state CIOs, chief information

14:20.066 --> 14:23.866 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
officers, and other agencies
are now stepping up to say this
is a real threat and we need

14:23.866 --> 14:25.933 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
to be able to
treat it seriously.

14:25.933 --> 14:30.833 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Since this
