14:46.166 --> 14:47.433 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
SEN.

14:47.433 --> 14:48.933 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
JAMES LANKFORD: It was
handled appropriately.

14:48.933 --> 14:50.566 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
