14:54.500 --> 14:58.533 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
The fact that in the earliest
days Michael Flynn was there
and that there were some people

14:58.533 --> 15:01.800 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
from the previous administration
that didn't like Michael
Flynn or thought that he had

15:01.800 --> 15:05.733 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
been challenged before, this
administration, the current
administration, was still trying

15:05.733 --> 15:10.000 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
to determine that, and to be
