15:22.933 --> 15:26.900 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: This also
seems to -- from an outsider's
perspective, even when it comes

15:28.866 --> 15:31.800 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
