country first and not party.

15:39.933 --> 15:40.933 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
SEN.

15:40.933 --> 15:43.000 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
JAMES LANKFORD: Correct.

15:43.000 --> 15:45.000 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And you would also assume that
there is a way to be able to
interpret that information.

15:45.000 --> 15:47.933 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And at times, you see an
accusation that may be released
out, for instance, with Michael

15:47.933 --> 15:52.666 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Flynn, to say he might have
been compromised, he might have
been vulnerable to blackmail.

15:52.666 --> 15:56.133 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
When you actually see that
information, I think a lot of
Americans will look at it and

15:56.133 --> 15:58.066 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
