are they talking about?

15:58.066 --> 16:01.066 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
One analyst will look at one
thing and see it one way.

16:01.066 --> 16:03.900 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
Another analyst will
look at it and see it an
entirely different way.

16:03.900 --> 16:07.966 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
There's more open to
interpretation here than
what the Americans are
being led to believe

16:07.966 --> 16:09.366 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
in this by that story.

16:09.366 --> 16:11.400 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
I would just tell people
to take a deep breath.

16:11.400 --> 16:15.633 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Let's not try to revise history
of what was actually going on
in literally the very first

16:15.633 --> 16:18.433 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
