greater sense of alarm?

16:56.233 --> 16:57.466 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
SEN.

16:57.466 --> 16:59.433 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
JAMES LANKFORD:
