17:12.800 --> 17:15.933 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
We are walking through
all the investigations
in a very bipartisan way.

17:15.933 --> 17:19.666 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
The Senate Intelligence
Committee is a very bipartisan
committee where we try to look

17:19.666 --> 17:21.666 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
