about national security
behind closed doors.

17:27.066 --> 17:29.100 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
And I think that's the
way that it should be.

17:29.100 --> 17:33.300 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: The White
House is supposed to announce,
