the request that we would
receive those recordings.

17:52.333 --> 17:54.400 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
It would clear up a
lot of the issues.

17:54.400 --> 17:58.933 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
Obviously, the former
FBI director, Jim Comey,
said he released out
his memos that were of

18:01.033 --> 18:04.366 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
