out anyway to try to proactively

18:04.366 --> 18:05.600 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
cut that off.

18:05.600 --> 18:07.833 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
I wish he wouldn't
have done that.

18:07.833 --> 18:11.100 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
But if we have recordings, we
could get the recordings and
get all the information out

18:11.100 --> 18:13.066 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
there.

18:13.066 --> 18:15.533 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
But at this point, if there
is a recording, based on a
tweet from the president saying

18:15.533 --> 18:19.666 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
he -- that Jim Comey better
hope that there aren't, I
would, quite frankly, tell you,

18:19.666 --> 18:21.833 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
if the White House
has recordings, they
should release them.

